      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a functional, roadworthy daily driver. While the engine and transmission are operational and it remains reliable for everyday use, potential buyers should expect noticeable cosmetic wear both inside and out, as well as minor mechanical quirks consistent with its age and mileage. It is a solid choice for someone looking for affordable transportation who doesn't mind a car with some character and history.",
