    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and shows clear signs of its age and regular use. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, a small dent on the rear passenger door, and some minor paint fading on the hood from sun exposure. Inside, the cabin shows significant wear on the driver's seat and some light staining on the rear carpets, though all dashboard controls and electronics are fully functional. Mechanically, the car is a reliable driver, though it may require some routine maintenance soon to address minor suspension noise and ensure continued performance.",
