    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, I\u2019m so excited to share this absolute gem with you. This car is in such incredible shape\u2014it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It's been my pride and joy and has been pampered every single day. If you\u2019re looking for something that\u2019s basically brand new and a total dream to drive, you\u2019ve found it. I'd love for it to go to a great home, so feel free to reach out with any questions!",
