      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, showroom-quality vehicle that satisfies even the most discerning collector. This car has been meticulously kept in a climate-controlled environment and has never seen inclement weather. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like factory finish protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating, entirely free of stone chips, swirls, or door dings. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the premium leather remains supple and matte, the carpets are spotless, and every electronic feature operates with precision. Mechanically, the car is flawless, supported by a comprehensive binder of service records from authorized specialists. With zero curb rash on the wheels and a pristine undercarriage, this is a rare opportunity to acquire a turn-key masterpiece that looks and drives exactly as it did on the showroom floor.",
      "price": 48500.0,
